pageContext.claim: “A lot of newspapers are endorsing us, because they know that Joe Biden is not up to this job.”
pageContext.analysis: Biden won the endorsements of 47 major newspapers, compared to 7 for Trump, while 44 made no endorsement, [according to an accounting by The American Presidency Project. Still, for Trump that was an improvement over 2016, when only two of the top 100 newspapers endorsed him.
